skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my dad jokes
des: Ask Alexa to tell you My Dad jokes when you need a laugh and feel relax your mind or whenever you want fresh. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next joke. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
